How many laps do you have left?

67
00:05:15,105 --> 00:05:17,835
Eighty laps.

68
00:05:17,835 --> 00:05:20,540
You didn't play by the rules, so you deserve this.

69
00:05:20,540 --> 00:05:22,345
I know.

70
00:05:27,860 --> 00:05:30,795
Did you take care of what you wanted to do that day?

71
00:05:31,580 --> 00:05:34,020
That was the first day ever

72
00:05:34,020 --> 00:05:38,951
picking Jina over baseball.

73
00:05:38,951 --> 00:05:41,050
The whole time I was running,

74
00:05:41,050 --> 00:05:48,936
I realized that my heart was always Jina's.

75
00:05:52,130 --> 00:05:53,840
[It might be a contract, but for me, it's a real relationship.]

76
00:05:53,840 --> 00:06:01,020
Please stop criticizing Jina and support my love for her instead.

77
00:06:01,020 --> 00:06:05,065
So that we can start a real relationship.

78
00:06:05,065 --> 00:06:09,060
