82
00:07:06,190 --> 00:07:08,610
Why do you care?

83
00:07:12,595 --> 00:07:16,125
I'm still really mad at you,

84
00:07:16,125 --> 00:07:19,410
but I forgot to say this to you. So here I am.

85
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:28,500
If you had a hard time because of me all that time, I'm sorry.

86
00:07:30,203 --> 00:07:32,563
So please come back to school.

87
